title: 'GM Street’: Saturday Sit-down Week 16 (Ep. 208)
description:
The Ringer’s Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier run through the five games they are most intrigued by this week: Jacksonville Jaguars at San Francisco 49ers (7:15), Atlanta Falcons at New Orleans Saints (9:55), Seattle Seahawks at Dallas Cowboys (12:05), Los Angeles Rams at Tennessee Titans (14:05), and Cleveland Browns at Chicago Bears (18:45).
